    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to level 1 per MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device. RH < 1 demonstrated at all five worst-case operating points. The hemolysis power-law parameterization methodology, as further elaborated in the scalar stress surrogate literature indexed by the package reference identifier, supports the adequacy of the model form selection. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission decision.",
